               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssār “Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     4ra-188va)&#xD; I-1) Maskaram (fols. 4ra-35vc)&#xD; I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     36ra-63vc)&#xD; I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 64ra-92vc)&#xD; I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     93ra-127vc)&#xD; I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 128ra-162rc l.7)&#xD; I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     162ra l.8 - 188va)&#xD; - Za-ʾaqrabku māḥleta… “The song I am offering…”
                     (concluding prayer): fol. 188va &#xD; The commemorative notices are followed by
                     ʿarke-hymns&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
